text: The Orionids is the next meteor shower you might be able to see. Active from Oct. 2 to Nov. 7, it is expected to be at its peak from Monday night into Tuesday morning. https://t.co/oEiNPHa2UR

name: nytimes
text: Coronavirus cases in New Jersey, an early epicenter of the pandemic, are on the rise again, doubling over the last month to an average of more than 900 new positive tests a day. https://t.co/P4xIkVdmHP

name: nytimes
text: The Carnival Sensation, which was sailing with no guests and a skeleton crew, rescued 24 people on Saturday from a boat that was taking on water 37 miles off the coast of Palm Beach, Florida. https://t.co/iu68pmRHqy
